Class NastranSetReader

java.lang.Object

              de.iabg.mesh.io.NastranSetReader
All Implemented Interfaces:
KeyReader, java.io.Closeable, java.lang.Readable
public class NastranSetReader
extends java.io.FileReader
implements KeyReader

This implementation of KeyReader parses a Nastran file containing node subset data. Refer to MeshConnectionReader class API for more details. The Nastran file can contain node subset data pertaining to nodes or to elements. This reader only parses data from nodes. Refer to the latest version of the MSC.Nastran Quick Reference Guide for more information for the file format.

Version:
September 26, 2008
Author:
Adam C. Dick, BSE

importNodeKeyLists

public void importNodeKeyLists(KeyMap nodeKeyLists)
Description copied from interface: KeyReader
Clears the given lists of node names and replaces them with the data parsed from the internally stored file. This method should be called after KeyReader.readFile(), otherwise no data will be saved.
